\id 1TI 1 Timothy in Boko, Ross Jones 2/08
\h 1 Timↄtee
\toc1 Timↄtee lá sɛ̃́ia
\toc2 1 Timↄtee
\toc3 1Tim
\mt1 TIMƆTEE LÁ SƐ̃IA
\imt1 Yã́ pↄ́ kú láɛ bee guuↄ
\ip Timↄtee daá Yudaɛ, aà maeá Gɛlɛkiɛ. Aa kↄ̃'è ń Pↄluo Lisita pↄ́ kú bùsu pↄ́ wì mɛ tia Tuukii guu, Pↄlupi wɛ̃́lɛgɛa plaade guu (Zĩn 16.1-3). Timↄtee gↄ̃̀ Pↄlu ìwa pↄ́ ìↄ kãiaànↄ ũɛ. A tɛaàzi aà wɛ̃́lɛ dasiↄ gɛa guu, ↄ̃ Pↄlu ì aà zĩ gãli pↄ́ an yã́ↄ lɛ́ gɛ́ súsuoↄ guu. Ayãmɛto aà tↄ́ kú zĩnaↄ lá guu (17.14-15, 18.5, 19.22) ń lá pↄ́ Pↄlu kɛ̃̀ↄ guu (1Kln 4.17, 16.10-11, Flp 2.19-24, 1Tɛs 3.2-6) ń lá pãleↄ. Lá mɛ̀n pla pↄ́ a kɛ̃̀ Timↄteeɛ ń pↄ́ a kɛ̃̀ Tituɛo wì mɛ pàsitɛɛ láↄ, yã́zɛ pↄ́ a kàlɛkalɛ dↄaanaↄ ń pàsitɛɛↄnɛo yã́i.
\ip Timↄtee lá sɛ̃́ia lɛ́ yã́ dↄ̀ↄ àaↄ̃ ↄlↄwɛ̃ɛ:
\imq Sɛ̃́ia gĩa à lɛzà Yesudeↄwa zɛ́ kaaliↄ yã́i ń làasoo kpaanlaↄ ń Yudaↄ yã́ pↄ́ yãalɛa ń luadↄ̃sai yã́ pↄ́ gbɛ̃eↄ lɛ́ dadanɛ́o. Zɛ́ kaalipiↄ mɛ̀ dṹniaɛ bee pↄ́ↄ maao, wìli fↄ̃ Lua lèo, sema wa asiiyã dↄ̃ bàasio. Aa gbãakpà blɛeↄ tɛ̃boao ń gia nↄsɛi yã́o.
\imq Bee gbɛa lápi lousisiyã bↄↄlɛkɛ̀wɛ̃ɛ, kↄ̃kãaa yã́ↄ ń yã́ pↄ́ a maa Yesude dↄaanaↄ aaↄ kũaↄ.
\imq A láakĩi lápi lɛdà Timↄteewa lá à kũ̀ aà a zĩ pↄ́ Lua dàɛ kɛ, lá à kũ̀ à laaidↄ luanaaikɛnaↄwa, iↄ dɛ Lua zĩkɛn maa ũ (4.6).
\ip Wa fↄ̃ lápi kpaalɛ lɛɛ pla: Yãdanɛ pↄ́ dɛ Yesudeↄ ń ń dↄaanaↄ pↄ́ ũ (1-3) ń Timↄtee zĩa yã́ↄ (4-6).
\c 1
\s1 Yãdanɛdeↄ gbaa laai
\p 
\v 1 Mámɛmaa Pↄlu, Kilisi Yesu zĩna, lá Lua wá Suabana ń Kilisi Yesu pↄ́ wá wɛ́ dↄaàzipio dìlɛmɛɛwa,
\v 2 ma láɛ bee kɛ̃̀nɛ Timↄtee,\f + \fr 1.2 \ft Zĩn 16.1\f* ma nɛ'ia Yesu zɛ́ guu. Mae Lua ń wá Dii Kilisi Yesuo gbɛ̃kɛkɛnɛ ń sùuuo, aai n gba aafia.
\p 
\v 3 Lá ma naɛma gↄↄ pↄ́ málɛ gɛ́ Masedoni bùsuu, gↄ̃ Ɛfɛsɛ, ní onɛ́ aasu yã́ pↄ́ i kpaaĩ ń Lua yã́oo danɛ́ lↄo.
\v 4 Aasu laaidↄ fĩ ń deziↄ tↄ́ kↄ̃nwɛa pↄ́ lɛ́ vĩoowa lↄo, bee ì mↄ́ ń lɛkpaaoɛ. Ìli mↄ́ ń yã́ pↄ́ Lua lɛ́ yáwanↄoo, aà náaikɛa mɛ́ ì mↄò.
\v 5 Ma yã́pi dìlɛ kɛ́ aaↄ yekↄ̃i yã́iɛ, yeakↄ̃i pↄ́ ì bↄ nↄ̀sɛpua ń làasoodaadoũo ń luanaaikɛa mↄafilisaio guu.
\v 6 Gbɛ̃eↄ pã̀alɛ yã́piↄnɛ aa pɛ̀lɛ yã́ àisai bↄlɛau.
\v 7 Aa ye wàↄ dɛ Mↄizi ikoyãdanɛdeↄ ũ, ãma aa yã́ pↄ́ wàlɛ o dↄ̃o ge yã́ pↄ́ wà zɛ̀wàↄ.
\p 
\v 8 Wá dↄ̃ ikoyãpi maa, tó gbɛ̃́ lɛ́ zĩkɛwà a zɛ́u,
\v 9 asa wá dↄ̃ kɛ́ Lua i ikoyã dilɛ gbɛ̃maa yã́io, sema yãdansaiↄ ń swã́gbãadeↄ ń lousisinsaiↄ ń duunkɛnaↄ ń luayãdansaiↄ ń dṹnia gbɛ̃́ↄ ń de ń dao dɛnaↄ ń gbɛ̃dɛnaↄ
\v 10 ń gbãsĩkɛnaↄ ń gↄ̃ɛ pↄ́ aaì gbãsĩkɛ ń ń gↄ̃ɛ deeoↄ ń gbɛ̃nazĩnyianaↄ ń ɛɛdeↄ ń yãdↄmadeↄ ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aaì bↄ yã́zɛde kpɛↄ píi.
\v 11 Yã́zɛdepi mɛ́ baona gawide pↄ́ Lua Báaade gↄ̃̀mɛɛ zĩ́ ũ.
\s1 Lá Lua gbɛ̃kɛkɛ̀ Pↄluɛ
\p 
\v 12 Ma Kilisi Yesu wá Dii pↄ́ ma gba gbãa sáaukɛ̀, asa à ma náaikɛ̀ à zĩdàmɛɛ.
\v 13 Ma aà tↄbɛ̃ɛsì yãa, ma ĩadà aà gbɛ̃́ↄwa,\f + \fr 1.13 \ft Zĩn 8.3, 9.4-5\f* ma gbãablèmá. Ń beeo à wɛ̃nadↄ̃̀mɛɛ, asa má kɛ̀ wɛ́siakɛ ń aà náaikɛsaio guuɛ.
\v 14 Ɔ̃ wá Dii Kilisi Yesu gbɛ̃kɛkɛ̀mɛɛ zↄ̃ↄ, a tò ma a náaikɛ̀, míↄ ye gbɛ̃́i naawa guu.
\v 15 Yã́ɛ bee sĩana vĩ wà sí. Kilisi Yesu mↄ̀ dṹnia guu duunkɛnaↄ suabaa yã́iɛ. Mapi, ma pↄ́ mɛ́ dɛ dãↄla,
\v 16 ↄ̃ Lua ma wɛ̃nagwà, kɛ́ mɛna zↄ̃ↄ pↄ́ Kilisi Yesu kɛ̀ ń ma gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ma duuna dɛńlao bↄ gupuau seela ũ gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aa aà náaikɛ aa wɛ̃ni láasai eↄnɛ.
\v 17 Lua mɛ̀ndona, gↄↄpii Kía pↄ́ lí gao mɛ́ wìli e ń wɛ́oo mɛ́ aↄ bɛɛɛ vĩ ń gawio gↄↄpii, ãmi.
\p 
\v 18 Ma nɛ́ Timↄtee, lá wà dↄ̀aa ãnabikɛkɛ̀ n yã́ musu, málɛ yã́pi danɛ kɛ́ ǹyↄ̃ kũa, ní zĩ̀ maa kaò
\v 19 luanaaikɛa guu ń làasoodaadoũo. Làasoodaadoũ lí kɛ gbɛ̃eↄnɛ yãe ũo, ↄ̃ an luanaaikɛa ì ↄ̃̀ↄkpa.
\v 20 Imɛnɛ ń Alɛsãndao kú ń guu. Ma ń kpá Setãuwa\f + \fr 1.20 \ft 1Kln 5.5\f* kɛ́ aaↄ dↄ̃ wìli dↄ́ɛ ń Luaoo.
\c 2
\s1 Lousisia
\p 
\v 1 Too, gĩa sɛ̃́ia málɛ lɛdama à wabikɛ gbɛ̃́piiɛ, à zɛ́ gbɛanɛ́, à kulɛkɛnɛ́ Luaɛ ń sáaukpaao.
\v 2 À wabikɛ kíaↄnɛ ń gbãadeↄ píi, kɛ́ wà e wàↄ ku aafia yãkelesai luayãmanaↄ ũ, wá kua iↄ gbia.
\v 3 Bee mɛ́ maa, ì ka Lua wá Suabanagu.
\v 4 A ye gbɛ̃́pii suaba, aai sĩana dↄ̃.
\v 5 Asa Lua mɛ̀ndoɛ, mɛ́ kↄ́ↄ kú mɛ̀ndo Lua ń gbɛ̃nazĩnaↄ zãnguo, ↄ̃n gbɛ̃nazĩna Kilisi Yesu ũ.\f + \fr 2.5 \ft Zĩn 4.12\f*
\v 6 À azĩa kpà gbɛ̃́pii fĩabobↄ ũ a gↄↄwa, Lua pↄeãpi seela ũ.
\v 7 Ayãmɛto Lua ma dilɛ a kpàwakɛna ũ, a zĩna ũ, mà a zɛ́ sĩande da buipãleↄnɛ.\f + \fr 2.7 \ft 2Tim 1.11\f* Sĩana málɛ o, i kɛ ɛɛ no.
\p 
\v 8 Má ye gↄ̃ɛↄ lousisi gu ń guo píi, aa ↄsɛ musu\f + \fr 2.8 \ft Bↄa 9.29\f* gbãsĩsai, pↄkũma ń lɛkpaao sai.
\v 9 Má ye lↄ nↄɛↄ ńzĩa kɛkɛ a zɛ́wa yↄ̃̀ↄsai zĩamↄnɛ sai. I kɛ ń mì yↄ̃̀ↄde tãao ge vua ń òso nↄamblebↄↄ ge zwã̀a ↄdeↄ no.\f + \fr 2.9 \ft 1Piɛ 3.3\f*
\v 10 Aa ńzĩa kɛkɛ ń maakɛao, lá a maa nↄɛ lousisinaↄ kɛwa.
\v 11 Nↄɛↄ yãdada kílikili, aa misiilɛ yã́pii musu.
\v 12 Mili we nↄɛↄ yãdàda gↄ̃ɛↄnɛ ge aaↄ iko vĩmáo, sema aaↄ ku kílikili.
\v 13 Asa Adamu ↄ̃ Lua kɛ̀ sɛ̃́ia, a gbɛa Ɛva.\f + \fr 2.13 \ft Daa 2.7, 21-22\f*
\v 14 I kɛ Adamu wa sã̀são, nↄɛ wa sã̀sã, à sì duunau.\f + \fr 2.14 \ft Daa 3.1-6\f*
\v 15 Tó nↄɛ wɛtã̀ ń luanaaikɛao ń yea gbɛ̃́ↄzio ń kuaadoakɛo zĩamↄnɛ sai, ali nɛ'i aafia.
\c 3
\s1 Gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄ ń dↄnlɛdeↄ
\p 
\v 1 Yã́ɛ bee sĩana vĩ: Tó gbɛ̃́ ye kɛ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ ũ, àlɛ zĩ maa nidɛ.
\v 2 Gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ líↄ ku tàaesai nↄmɛndode ũ, laaide ũ, ìↄ azĩa kũa dↄ̃ gbɛ̃́ dↄ̀ↄde ũ, nibↄfↄ̃na ũ, gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ a fↄ̃ yãdanɛ́ ũ.
\v 3 Asu àↄ dɛ igbɛ̃na ge gbɛ̃́ pãsĩ ũo. Aàↄ dɛ nↄ̀sɛdoũde yãkelesaide ũ. Ɔ̃a su dↄaaɛ̀o.
\v 4 Aàↄ a ua kũa dↄ̃, aà nɛ́ↄ lí misiilɛɛ̀ aaliↄ aà ↄtondↄkĩi gwa.\f + \fr 3.4 \ft Tit 1.6-8\f*
\v 5 Asa tó gbɛ̃́ a ua kũa dↄ̃o, kpelewa a fↄ̃ ↄlia Lua gãlideↄzii?
\v 6 Asu àↄ dɛ gbɛ̃́ dafuna ũo, kɛ́ asu ĩ́anadã, i azĩa dayãu lán Ibiisiwao yã́i.
\v 7 Aà tↄ́ àↄ na Yesusaideↄ kĩ́i lↄ, kɛ́ wasu aà tↄ́'ĩisi, i zu Ibiisi bauo yã́i.
\p 
\v 8 Màa lↄ dↄnlɛdeↄ aaↄ dɛ gbɛ̃́ gbiaↄ ũ. Aasu wàↄ dɛ lɛplaadeↄ ũo. Wɛ̃ yã́ su dↄaanɛ́o. Aasu wàↄ dɛ ↄwɛɛlɛmbɛ̃ɛↄ ũo.
\v 9 Aaↄ Yesu yã́ kũa ń làasoodaadoũo.
\v 10 Wà ń yã́ gwa gĩa, tó wi yãe emáo, wi gbasa ń dilɛ dↄnlɛdeↄ ũ.
\v 11 Màaɛ ń nↄɛↄ. Aaↄ dɛ nↄɛ gbiaↄ ũ, laaideↄ ũ, aaìↄ náai vĩ yã́pii guu. Aasu wàↄ dɛ gudɛnaↄ ũo.
\v 12 Dↄnlɛde àↄ dɛ nↄmɛndode ũɛ, aàↄ a ua ń a nɛ́ↄ kũa dↄ̃.
\v 13 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ zĩkɛ̀ a zɛ́wa, ì zɛkĩi maa e, aà sↄ̃ iↄ dilɛa a Kilisi Yesu náaikɛa guu maamaa.
\p 
\v 14 Baa kɛ́ málɛ yã́piↄ onɛ, má dìlɛ má mↄ́ n gwai tia.
\v 15 Tó ma mↄa su lɛ́ gɛ̃gɛ̃ɛ, má ye ǹyↄ̃ dↄ̃ lá a maa wàↄ ku Lua uadeↄ ũɛ. Wámɛ wá Lua bɛ̃́ɛ gãlideↄ ũ, sĩana zĩ́mpɛlɛ ń a gbãa'ekĩio ũ.
\v 16 Lua asiiyã pↄ́ bↄ̀ gupuau zↄ̃ↄ sĩanaɛ:
\q1 À mↄ̀ gbɛ̃nazĩna ũ,
\q1 Lua Nisĩna aà sĩandekɛ ↄ̀lↄnɛ́,
\q1 malaikaↄ aà è.
\q1 Wà aà yã́ waasokɛ̀ buiↄ guu,
\q1 wà aà náaikɛ̀ dṹnia guu,
\q1 Lua aà sɛ̀ tàò a kĩ́i gawi guu.
\c 4
\s1 Tɛ̃ yã́
\p 
\v 1 Lua Nisĩna ò wásawasa, gↄↄgbɛzãzĩ gbɛ̃eↄ pãkpa Yesu zɛ́i, aai tɛ sã́sãyã pↄ́ tã́a ì ɛɛdeↄ da a oauzi.
\v 2 Ɛɛde mↄafilide pↄ́ vãi lí kã̀adańlaoↄ mɛ́ aa ń sãsã.
\v 3 Aaì gí gbɛ̃́ↄnɛ aa nↄsɛ aa zãkɛ, mɛ́ aaì blɛ tɛ̃́nɛ́, blɛ pↄ́ Lua kɛ̀ a náaikɛna pↄ́ aa sĩana dↄ̃ↄnɛ aa ble ń a sáaukpaao.
\v 4 Pↄ́ pↄ́ Lua kɛ̀ píi maaɛ.\f + \fr 4.4 \ft Daa 1.31\f* Wásu a kee tɛ̃boo,\f + \fr 4.4 \ft Maa 7.19\f* wà ble ń aà sáaukpaao,
\v 5 asa Lua yã́ ń wá wabikɛao gbãbↄ̀ɛ̀.
\s1 Kilisi Yesu zĩkɛn maa
\p 
\v 6 Tó n yã́piↄ dà n gbɛ̃́ↄnɛ, ńyↄ̃ↄ dɛ Kilisi Yesu zĩkɛn maa ũ, asa ńlɛ nzĩa gwa ń Yesu yã́o, ń tɛ́ yãmaa pↄ́ wa dànɛi.
\v 7 Mikɛ̃ fɛlɛkaa fĩ pↄ́ lí kpaaĩ ń Lua yã́oowa. Ǹ nzĩa toto, kɛ́ ǹyↄ̃ dɛ luayãmana ũ.
\v 8 Mɛtotoa ài vĩ yↄↄ, ãma dɛa luayãmana ũ ài vĩ yã́pii guuɛ, asa bee ì mↄ́ ń wɛ̃nio gbã ń ziao.
\v 9 Yã́pi sĩana vĩ, à kà wà si ↄplapla,
\v 10 wí zĩkɛ wà dɛ̃ɛka a musu. Wá wɛ́ dↄ Lua bɛ̃́ɛzi. Ɔ̃mɛ gbɛ̃́pii Suabana ũ, azaiasa aà náaikɛnaↄ.
\p 
\v 11 Yã́piↄ dilɛnɛ́, ní dadanɛ́.
\v 12 Ńsu to wà saka n ɛ̀waasokɛguo. To n kua zɛ'ↄlↄ Yesudeↄnɛ yã'oa ń yãkɛao ń yeakↄ̃io ń luanaaikɛao ń kua gbãsĩsaio guu.
\v 13 E màↄ mↄ́, wɛtã ń Lua yã́ kyokɛao, ní danɛ́, ní lɛdaomá.
\v 14 Gba pↄ́ Lua dànɛ gↄↄ pↄ́ wà ãnabikɛkɛ̀ n yã́ musu, mɛ́ gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄↄ ↄnàma, ńsu niazĩkpaio.
\v 15 Laaidↄ yã́piↄwa, ní mɛkpawà, gbɛ̃́pii i n gɛa'aɛ e.
\v 16 Ǹ nzĩa yã́ ń n yãdanɛo tàasika. Zɛ súsu ń yã́piↄ. Tó ń kɛ̀ màa, ńyↄ̃ nzĩa suaba ń gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aalɛ swã́sɛ n yã́iↄ.
\c 5
\s1 Gyaaↄ ń dↄaanaↄ
\p 
\v 1 Ńsu maezↄ̃ↄ leleo.\f + \fr 5.1 \ft Lev 19.32\f* Lɛdawà n mae ũ, ní da ɛ̀waasoↄwa n vĩ̀i ń n dãunaↄ ũ.
\v 2 Lɛda nↄɛzↄ̃ↄwa n da ũ, ní da nↄgbãa ge wɛ̃́ndiawa n dãe ũ làasooplasai.
\p 
\v 3 Gyaa gbɛ̃andoↄ kpɛla.
\v 4 Tó gyaa nɛ́ↄ ge tↄũnaↄ vĩ, aa ń daɛↄ gwaa dada gĩa, aai fĩabo ń maeↄ ń ń daↄnɛ, asa bee ì ka Luagu.
\v 5 Gyaa gbɛ̃ando wɛ́ ìↄ dↄ Luazi, ì wɛtã lousisia ń wabikɛaowa gwãasĩna ń fãanɛo.
\v 6 Gyaa pãpãkɛnaá gɛɛ, baa tó a bɛ̃́ɛ.
\v 7 Yã́piↄ danɛ́, kɛ́ wasu ń tàae eo.
\v 8 Tó gbɛ̃́ lɛ́ a daɛↄ gwao, atɛ̃sa aà uadeↄ, à bↄ̀ Lua yã́ kpɛɛ, Yesusaide dɛaàla.
\v 9 Nↄɛ pↄ́ dɛ wà da gyaaↄ guun kɛ: Nↄɛ pↄ́ kà wɛ̃̀ bàaↄ̃ mɛ́ à zãkɛ̀ gɛ̃n do,
\v 10 wìↄ aà dↄ̃ maakɛna ũ, nɛgwan maa ũ, nibↄfↄ̃na pↄ́ Lua gbɛ̃́ↄ gbá pìpi ũ, taasideↄ dↄnlɛde ũ, nↄɛ pↄ́ mɛkpà maakɛa píiwa ũ.
\v 11 Ńsu gyaa nↄgbãaↄ dauo, asa tó an gↄ̃ nidɛa fɛ̀lɛ, an naa Kilisiwa a busaɛ, aaiↄ ye zãkɛ,
\v 12 aai ńzĩa dayãu, kɛ́ aa lɛ́ pↄ́ aa gbɛ̃̀ɛ̀ yãa gbòo yã́i.
\v 13 Bee gbɛa aaì pãkɛ dada, aaìↄ bɛbɛ wàↄ ualɛkɛ. I kɛ màaden ń ũ adoo, aaì gↄ̃ gbɛ̃pen gudɛnaↄ ũɛ, aaì yã́ pↄ́ dɛ wà oo o.
\v 14 Ayãmɛto má ye gyaa nↄgbãaↄ zãkɛ, aai nɛ'i, aai laaidↄ bɛwa, kɛ́ aasu wá ibɛɛↄ gba zɛ́ aa wá tↄbɛ̃ɛsio yã́i.
\v 15 An gbɛ̃eↄ bↄ̀ tɛ Setãuzi kↄ̀.
\v 16 Tó Yesudee gyaaↄ vĩ a bɛ, aàli dↄńlɛ. Asu to aa gↄ̃ gãlideↄnɛ aso ũo, kɛ́ aa e dↄ gyaa gbɛ̃andoↄlɛ yã́i.
\p 
\v 17 Gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ pↄ́ ì dↄaa a zɛ́wa kà wà fĩaboɛ̀ lɛɛ pla, atɛ̃sa gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ waasokɛa ń yãdaanɛ́o ãia vĩ.
\v 18 Wà yã́ɛ bee kɛ̃̀ láu wà mɛ̀: Ásuli lɛsↄkpa zu pↄ́ lɛ́ pↄgbɛ̃ɛo.\f + \fr 5.18 \ft Iko 25.4, 1Kln 9.9\f* Wà mɛ̀ lↄ: Zĩkɛna kà à a asea e.\f + \fr 5.18 \ft Luk 10.7\f*
\v 19 Ńsu gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ mↄ̀ ń gbɛ̃zↄ̃ↄ káalao yã́ sio, sema seeladeↄ kà gbɛ̃ↄn pla ge àaↄ̃ bàasio.\f + \fr 5.19 \ft Iko 19.15\f*
\v 20 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ duunakɛ̀ↄ gba laai gbɛ̃́pii wáa, kɛ́ vĩa e gbɛ̃́ kĩniↄ kṹ.
\v 21 Ma nanɛ Lua ń Kilisi Yesuozi ń malaika pↄ́ à ń sɛ́ↄ, ǹyↄ̃ yã́piↄ kũa gbɛ̃e tɛ̃bosai. Ńsu yãe kɛ gbɛ̃eɛ ublembɛkɛa yã́io.
\v 22 Ńsu wã ↄna gbɛ̃́wa ǹ aà dazĩuo. Ńsu to n lɛ́ àↄ ku gbɛ̃e duunauo. Ǹyↄ̃ nzĩa kũa gbãsĩsai.
\v 23 Ńsu í pã mi ado lↄo. Nìli vɛ̃ɛ ga yↄↄ n nↄ̀sɛ ń n gyãkɛa mↄ̀ↄmↄↄo yã́i.
\p 
\v 24 Gbɛ̃eↄ duuna ì bↄ gupuau e wàↄ gɛ́ a yãkɛkɛińnↄ, gbɛ̃eↄ pↄ́ sↄ̃, ìli bↄ kpaao.
\v 25 Màa lↄ maakɛa ì bↄ gupuau, baa a pↄ́ wi eo a e gↄ̃ ulɛao.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ dɛ zↄ ũↄ ń diiↄ dilɛ gbia, aai misiilɛnɛ́ yã́pii guu, kɛ́ wasu Lua tↄ́ ń yã́ pↄ́ wi danɛ́o bɛ̃̀ɛboo yã́i.
\v 2 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ an diiↄ dɛ Yesude ũↄ su dↄ́ɛmá kɛ́ aa dɛ kↄ̃gbɛ̃ↄ ũ yã́io. Aa zↄblenɛ́ maamaa, asa gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ aalɛ ń zĩ baa bleↄ dɛ Yesudeↄ ũɛ, an gbɛ̃́ yenzideↄ ũ. Yã́piↄ danɛ́, ní lɛdaomá.
\s1 Yea ↄ̃ai
\p 
\v 3 Tó gbɛ̃e lɛ́ yãpãle danɛ́ mɛ́ i zɛ ń wá Dii Yesu Kilisi yã́ sĩandeo ń wá zɛ́ yãdanɛoo,
\v 4 yↄ̃̀ↄdeɛ, a yãe dↄ̃o, lɛkpaa gii ń yãgwaa láasaio aà kũ̀ gyã ũ. Yã́ beeↄ ì to gbɛ̃́ↄ wɛdↄkↄ̃ɛ, aaì sòlekɛ, aaì kↄ̃ sↄ̃́sↄ̃, aaì làasoo vãi sɛ́ ń kↄ̃o,
\v 5 aaìↄ kĩ́iwãi vĩ. Gbɛ̃́piↄ làasoo kolea, sĩana pìlimá, aaìↄ e lousisiaá ↄwɛɛlɛzɛɛ.
\v 6 Lousisia ài zↄ̃ↄ sĩana, tó gbɛ̃́ zɛ̀ ń pↄ́ pↄ́ á vĩo.
\v 7 Wi mↄ́ ń pↄeo dṹnia guu lao, mɛ́ wá e tá ń pↄeoo.
\v 8 Tó wá pↄblea ń pↄkasaↄ vĩ, bee mↄ̀.
\v 9 Gbɛ̃́ pↄ́ ye gↄ̃ ↄde ũↄ ì ńzĩa da yↄ̃a bau. Pↄ́ nidɛa mìsai kaide ì gɛ̃ńgu, i ń kpálɛ músi ń kaalɛo guu.
\v 10 Yea ↄ̃ai mɛ́ yãvãi píi zĩ́na ũ. Gbɛ̃eↄ lɛ́ a kↄ̃dɛ e aa gɛ̀ zã̀ò Yesu zɛ́wa, aa wãwã zↄ̃ↄ kpà ńzĩai.
\s1 Dɛ̃ɛ maa ká
\p 
\v 11 Lá Lua gbɛ̃́n n ũ, bàalɛ yã́piↄnɛ, ní tó yãmaa líↄ dↄaanɛ ń yã́ pↄ́ zɛvĩ Luaɛo ń aà náaikɛao ń yea gbɛ̃́ↄzio ń mɛnao ń nↄ̀sɛniɛo.
\v 12 Dɛ̃ɛ maa ká n Yesu náaikɛa guu, ní wɛ̃ni láasai e, asa ↄ̃ Lua n sisiwà gↄↄ pↄ́ n lɛ́ maa gbɛ̃̀ɛ̀ bíla wáa.
\v 13 Ma nanɛ Lua pↄ́ ì wɛ̃ni kpa pↄ́piiwazi ń Kilisi Yesu pↄ́ yãmaa ò Pↄ̃nsi Pilatiɛo,\f + \fr 6.13 \ft Zãa 18.36-37\f*
\v 14 ǹyↄ̃ yã́ pↄ́ wa dìlɛnɛ kũa sãasai tàaesai e wá Dii Yesu Kilisi mↄ́zĩ.
\v 15 Gbãade mɛ̀ndona Báaade, kíaↄ Kía, diiↄ Dii mɛ́ a Kilisipi bↄ a gↄↄwa.\f + \fr 6.15 \ft Zia 19.16\f*
\v 16 Ɔ̃mɛ lí gao ado, ìↄ ku gupua pↄ́ wìli fↄ̃ sↄ̃̀io guu.\f + \fr 6.16 \ft Soũ 104.2\f* Gbɛ̃e i wɛsiaàlɛo, wa fↄ̃ seo.\f + \fr 6.16 \ft Bↄa 33.20\f* Ɔ̃mɛ gawi ń gbãao vĩ gↄↄpii, ãmi.
\p 
\v 17 O dṹnia tiaɛ bee ↄdeↄnɛ aasu ĩ́anadão. Aasu gbãa'e ↄda náaisaiwao, aa gbãa'e Lua pↄ́ ì pↄ́pii kpáwá zↄ̃ↄ wà pↄnakɛòwa.
\v 18 Onɛ́ aa maakɛ, maakɛa i tↄ̃́má. Aaↄ dɛ gbadanaↄ ũ, aaiↄ gbɛ̃kɛ vĩ.
\v 19 Beewa aa kũ̀sũa maa di ńzĩaɛ àizãna pↄ́ ũ,\f + \fr 6.19 \ft Mat 6.20\f* aai wɛ̃ni pↄ́ dɛ wɛ̃ni ũ sĩana e.
\p 
\v 20 Timↄtee, kàeda yã́ pↄ́ Lua nànɛ n ↄzĩi. Ɛ̃ dṹnia yã́ giiↄnɛ ń yãwaaipaa pↄ́ wì mɛ dↄ̃aɛo.
\v 21 Gbɛ̃eↄ zɛ̀ò, ↄ̃ aa pã̀alɛ Yesu zɛ́ɛ.
\p Lua gbɛ̃kɛkɛɛ́.
